{"tid":749752,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 孤兒瘋人院","createTime":"2018-07-20T09:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T09:32:21.000Z","uid":171592,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e393507f57e45662cf04cafe84833378702be51","tid":749752,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"孤兒瘋人院   <br />\n專收集一堆說話太瘋癲而被踢或者鍾意玩狼人既孤兒，隨意傾談你既所思所想,<br />\n以下人士請勿內進:<br />\n- 23歲以下人士  <br />\n- 搵食人士即踢   <br />\n- 狗公麻煩走啦    <br />\n- 娘娘行遠啲呀  <br />\n<br />\n我地谷內已有專屬狗公、娘娘、搵食人士，佢地會不斷監察，以防有人威脅到佢地既地位。 <br />\n每個月會清一次深潛人士，拒絕cdrom，大家有心想傾計先入，谷內有來自各行各業既人，想傾乜都可以，只怕你開唔到題。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DTw_jUqihgm_OcDbJSIYFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDTw_jUqihgm_OcDbJSIYFA&d=GFpYaXrnPOrAikmqtyFSsjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a6b28c3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DTw_jUqihgm_OcDbJSIYFA</a>"}]}